Package: shlama
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: curl, jq
Maintainer: xt67 <xt67@github.com>
Description: Your terminal llama - Natural language to shell commands
 shlama is a CLI tool that converts natural language into safe Linux
 shell commands using a local LLM (Ollama). You ask for something,
 it suggests a command, and you approve before execution.
 .
 No cloud. No API keys. Just your shell and a llama.
Homepage: https://github.com/xt67/shlama
